summary: This script creates a directory named "deps", navigates to the "go-cqhttp" folder, sets GOPATH and GOPROXY variables, then builds the code using go build.

details.comment: This script creates a directory named "deps", navigates to the "go-cqhttp" folder, sets GOPATH and GOPROXY variables, then builds the code using go build.
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
mkdir deps
cd go-cqhttp
GOPATH=$PWD/../deps GOPROXY=https://goproxy.cn,direct go build
